description._content: Original Collection: Extension and Experiment Station Communications Photograph Collection (P120) Item Number: P120:2806 Image Description: Mrs. Dorothy Burleson, Walla Walla nurse at Athena and Milton-Freewater farm labor camps, treating a Mexican National in a trailer dispensary at the Athena camp.
